# Project Context

**Client:** Junior Solice — It's Just June Pest Control, Bergen County, NJ.

**Stack:** Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS. No React, Vite, or Tailwind unless the user explicitly requests it.

**Repo:** https://github.com/SWFTstudios/itsjustjunepestcontrol.git

**Entry point:** `index.html` (monolith today; target layout uses `assets/` — see `asset-migration.mdc`).

## Section map

| ID | Content |
|----|---------|
| `#hero` | Headline, bullets, CTAs, hero photo placeholder |
| `#services` | 6 pest service cards |
| `#testimonials` | Review marquee (`#marqueeTrack`) |
| `#areas` | Bergen County towns |
| `#how` | 3-step process |
| `#why` | Value props + founder quote |
| `#about` | Junior bio + photo placeholder |
| `#quoteModal` | Appointment form modal |

## Placeholders (do not treat as production-ready)

- Phone: `(201) 555-0000` / `tel:+12015550000` — replace before launch
- Email: `hello@itsjustjune.com` — real
- Form: `handleSubmit` fakes success; inputs lack `name` attributes
- Images: emoji placeholders in hero and about sections
- Footer: Privacy/Terms link to `#`

## Conventions

- Minimize diff scope; match existing patterns in `index.html`
- Preserve brand spelling: **It's Just June**
- Commit only when the user asks; no force-push to `main`
- Read `INSTRUCTIONS.md` for prioritized todos
